ds.made.jdbc.easy

Class EasyCallForStoredProcedure<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ds.made.jdbc.easy.EasyCallForStoredProcedure<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Any simple EasyRow / EasyColumn annotated class or Object.class.

    public class EasyCallForStoredProcedure<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Simple stored procedure (cursor/out parameters) to List mapper.
    Can make also direct class instances if the setOtherClassFields configuration is set.
    Can be used for procedures / functions with in out / out parameters. Use Object for generic and Object.class for class type.
    Author:
    ds
